|                       |                       | function that takes   |
| Required              |                       | no arguments; when a  |
|                       |                       | cancellation is       |
|                       |                       | requested, the        |
|                       |                       | function being        |
|                       |                       | executed by           |
|                       |                       | taskProvider should   |
|                       |                       | wrap up and return    |
|                       |                       | ASAP.                 |
+-----------------------+-----------------------+-----------------------+

