Rect Object Type

 Rect accepts numeric pixel values to describe how far to extend a
rectangular area. These values are added to the original area's size to
expand it.

Example 

    {
        bottom: 20,
        left: null,
        right: undefined,
        top: 50
    }

 

Keys and values 

 bottom 

  Type                         Required
  ---------------------------- ----------
  number,  null ,  undefined   No

 left 

  Type                         Required
  ---------------------------- ----------
  number,  null ,  undefined   No

 right 

  Type                         Required
  ---------------------------- ----------
  number,  null ,  undefined   No

 top 

  Type                         Required
  ---------------------------- ----------
  number,  null ,  undefined   No

Used by 

-    Image
-    Pressable
-    Text
-    TouchableWithoutFeedback

